oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Smokey Smith Show - Openings w/ KRNT sign-on
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three cuts of the KRNT (Des Moines, IA) morning sign-on, followed by the opening to the Smokey Smith Show. Originally to be broadcast weekdays at 4:58 am. Content identical to TR001683_2.
